, (path plot) . , x .

temp_data <- tibble(
  x = sample(1:100, 25, replace = F),
  y = rnorm(25, 10, 2)
)
##  .
temp_data %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) + geom_line() + theme_bw()

##  .
temp_data %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) + geom_path() + theme_bw()

## x    .
temp_data %>%
  arrange(x) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) + geom_path() + theme_bw()

(Modifying Axes)

xlab(), ylab() labs() .

ggplot(mpg, aes(cty, hwy)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 1 / 3) +
  xlab("city driving (mpg)") +
  ylab("highway driving (mpg)") + 
  theme_bw()

#    /
ggplot(mpg, aes(cty, hwy)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 1 / 3) +
  xlab(NULL) +
  ylab(NULL) + 
  theme_bw()

# labs()       .
ggplot(mpg, aes(cty, hwy)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 1 / 3) +
  labs(x = "city driving (mpg)", y = "highway driving (mpg)") + 
  theme_bw()

. xlim(), ylim(), lims() .

ggplot(mpg, aes(drv, hwy)) +
  geom_jitter(width = 0.25) + theme_bw()

##     , hwy 20 30  .
ggplot(mpg, aes(drv, hwy)) +
  geom_jitter(width = 0.25) +
  lims(x = c("f", "r"), y = c(20, 30)) + 
  theme_bw()

##   ,  (, )   NA .   30  .
ggplot(mpg, aes(drv, hwy)) +
  geom_jitter(width = 0.25, na.rm = TRUE) +
  ylim(NA, 30) + theme_bw()

##       coord_cartisian()    .
ggplot(mpg, aes(drv, hwy)) +
  geom_jitter(width = 0.25) +
  coord_cartesian(y = c(20, 30)) + theme_bw()

##   .
presidential <- presidential %>%
  dplyr::filter(start > economics$date[1])
presidential
##       .
ggplot(economics) +
  geom_rect(
    aes(xmin = start, xmax = end, fill = party),
    ymin = -Inf, ymax = Inf, alpha = 0.2,
    data = presidential
  ) +
  geom_vline(
    aes(xintercept = as.numeric(start)),
    data = presidential,
    colour = "grey50", alpha = 0.5
  ) +
  geom_text(
    aes(x = start, y = 2500, label = name),
    data = presidential,
    size = 3, vjust = 0, hjust = 0, nudge_x = 50
  ) +
  geom_line(aes(date, unemploy)) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("blue", "red")) +
  theme_bw() + theme(legend.position = "top")

. , , , .

ggplot(mpg, aes(cty, hwy, color = factor(cyl))) + geom_jitter() +
  geom_abline(colour = "grey50", size = 2) + 
  labs(
    x = "City mileage/gallon",
    y = "Highway mileage/gallon",
    colour = "Cylinders",
    title = "Highway and city mileage are highly correlated"
  ) +
  scale_colour_brewer(type = "seq", palette = "Spectral") + 
  theme_bw() + 
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", size = 12),
    legend.background = 
      element_rect(fill = "white", size = 4, colour = "white"), 
    legend.justification = c(0, 1),
    legend.position = c(0, 1),
    axis.ticks = element_line(colour = "grey70", size = 0.2),
    panel.grid.major = element_line(colour = "grey70", size = 0.2), 
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank()
  )
